Thanks for using Structured!

This update brings some minor improvements and fixes, as well as translations for Swedisch and Croatian!

A big thanks to all the translators. If you'd like to help translate Structured, just reach out!

I'm also close to releasing a big update, Structured 2.0! It is already avaiable on TestFlight as a beta. If you want to help test it, just reach out!

Let me know if there are any problems, or you have any other suggestions!

Leo
